body: "Specific gaps found:\\n1. SDK.md missing: cli-contracts exports inventory (PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES, PM_TOOL_ACTIONS, PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA, withFlagAliasMetadata, toCompletionFlagString, Commander helpers)\\n2. EXTENSION_CAPABILITIES / EXTENSION_CAPABILITY_* not listed in SDK.md\\n3. EXTENSIONS.md: registerCommand + inline flags needs schema capability (not documented)\\n4. EXTENSIONS.md: registerExporter requires importers capability (same as importers) but not stated\\n5. ExtensionCommandArgumentDefinition not exported from SDK but used by CommandDefinition.arguments\\n6. CommandDefinition.handler should have @deprecated JSDoc annotation\\n7. ./cli package.json entry has empty type declarations"
